n Fogerty, The Hellacopters, The Meteors, Tygers of Pan Tang, Bloodlights, The Soulbreaker Company, Pat Capocci, Loquillo y Union Carbide Productions, así como Cheap Trick, Inglorius y Crank County Daredevils. EFEep/jlg>>
